Description: Time and weather announcement scripts for Asterisk
 Scripts to announce time and weather conditions through Asterisk.
 Supports both local and network weather stations, with caching
 and temperature conversion options. Time announcements support
 both 12 and 24-hour formats with optional weather reports.
 .
 Features include:
  * Time announcements in 12/24 hour format
  * Weather conditions from multiple data sources
  * Support for international airport codes
  * Configurable caching system
  * Comprehensive logging
  * Custom sound directory support 
